<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2020</DATELINE><TITLE>‘This beast is moving very fast.’ Will the new coronavirus be contained—or go pandemic?</TITLE><BODY>The silver lining of the epidemic is that scientists have collected and shared information at record speed. “Every day that goes by we know more and every day that goes by we can do better modeling,” Vespignani says. “Unfortunately, this beast is moving very fast.”&#3;</BODY></TEXT>